{"__ud_title":"Cent iOS快捷指令","__ud_tags":["Cent"],"__ud_update_time":1780312319036,"__ud_create_time":1778731472792,"__ud_draft":false,"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":"Cent-iOS快捷指令"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Cent iOS快捷指令"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"通过Cent iOS版可以使用下面的快捷指令快速进行记账，注意国行需要配合豆包app一起使用，后续开放Apple Intelligence后有希望换成原生接口。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://www.icloud.com/shortcuts/3a21355da0904507b6a30d330656b7d4","target":"_blank","rel":"noreferer","class":null}}],"text":"Cent截图记账豆包版"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"如果不想下载豆包，则必须要有一个支持Open AI格式的AI服务和key，例如智谱，然后使用这个快捷指令"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://www.icloud.com/shortcuts/c8bce7cfa05c4dc8a9d0227916ce1ff7","target":"_blank","rel":"noreferer","class":null}}],"text":"Cent记账智谱版"},{"type":"text","text":"，可以通过"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://glink25.github.io/post/%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AF-Cent-AI-%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%8E%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/","target":"_blank","rel":"noreferer","class":null}}],"text":"这篇文章"},{"type":"text","text":"查看如何获取AI服务和key。"}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"使用方式"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"使用方式"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1，控制中心"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"在控制中心中长按进入编辑状态，选择添加控制-快捷指令-运行快捷指令，然后在快捷指令中选择安装好的快捷指令，就可以通过下拉控制中心进行快速截图记账了，适合"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"2，Action Button"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"在支持Action Button的机型中，进入设置页面，在Action Button设置中选择运行快捷指令，选择安装好的快捷指令，就可以长按Action Button进行记账了。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"3，轻点背面"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"在iOS辅助功能-触控-轻点背面，选择轻点两下或者三下，再选择刚刚安装的快捷指令即可。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"注意如果使用2，3种方式，可以删掉快捷指令中的“等待”和“隐藏控制中心”动作，速度更快，或者直接使用下面的"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"link","attrs":{"href":"https://www.icloud.com/shortcuts/fffa4c7c646b473ab25558b551a6ded3","target":"_blank","rel":"noreferer","class":null}}],"text":"Cent截图记账豆包快速版"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"原理"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"原理"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"快捷指令通过识别当前截屏的文本，将文本发送给豆包进行分析，如何得到最终的账单并记录在Cent中，因此需要提前安装豆包App。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"如果你了解一些快捷指令搭建方法，也可以使用自己的AI大模型API进行替换。如果你希望个性化控制账单，例如调整备注、想要更加细致的分类等，也可以通过调整快捷指令中的提示词文本进行微调。"}]}]}